Package youtube.classes

Class Video

java.lang.Object
youtube.classes.Video
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Watchable
public class Video extends Object implements Serializable, Watchable
The Video class represents a video It stores basic information about the video (e.g such as video ID, name, description, duration, upload date, number of views, number of likes, and premium status) Implements Serializable for object serialization and Watchable for watchable items.

      thumbnail - The video's thumbnail image.
      name - The name of the video.
      description - The description of the video.
      duration - The duration of the video in seconds.
      dateOfUpload - The date when the video was uploaded.
